description: JPEG Issue 98: The University in Crisis Over the course of the fall semester of 2009, UC campuses responded to the budget crisis with protests that ranged from rallies, marches, teach-ins, sit-outs, to occupation of campus buildings. This special issue of the Kroeber Anthropological Society Journal brings together faculty and undergraduate student voices from spoken protest to print. Front Cover: PDF Contents: PDF Back Cover: PDF
title: JPEG
